  <brief_title>Can Peripheral NIRS Predict the Response to a Fluid Challenge in Pediatric Patients: An Interventional Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Can Peripheral NIRS Predict the Response to a Fluid Challenge in Pediatric Patients: An Interventional Study</official_title>
