  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will be conducted on pediatric patients up to 14 years of age. The effect of two&#xD;
      fluid challenge regimes on cerebral and peripheral NIRS will be assessed, in a randomized&#xD;
      double blinded controlled trial. The findings will be correlated with two ultrasound&#xD;
      measures, previously validated as markers of fluid responsiveness.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
